{"tid":2330853,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"大三罷藏打火機鐵鎚等工具 三青年罪成還柙候判","createTime":"2020-12-18T10:30:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-18T12:03:04.000Z","uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"6e703fe0681c1a2a0387856f587687ac08af4f97","tid":2330853,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T10:30:23.000Z","msg":"有網民於去年11月11日發起「大三罷」，堵塞各區交通。四名年輕男女被指當日凌晨在天水圍天瑞邨一帶管有索帶、打火機和鐵鎚等物品，被控管有物品意圖損壞財產等罪，其中三人經審訊後，今天被裁定罪成。裁判官下令各人還柙，其間索取多份報告再作判刑。<br />\n<br />\n水官續指，三名被告於凌晨時份攜帶涉案物品在街頭出現，而從新聞片段得悉，涉案物品於當時社會運動中是常被用作破壞的工具，認為三人確實有意圖進行破壞或作非法用途，故裁定三人罪成。<br />\n<br />\n水官下令先索取各人的勞教、教導所、更生中心及感化報告，又提醒被告不要存在太大幻想會判處感化令。水官下令三人還柙至明年1月4日判刑。"},{"pid":"e1ded1b3eb3c322f19ceae39ebd7650cf658c2b4","tid":2330853,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T10:30:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201218/FYXQRVQFXBAPFLM7FWFS75ZV3Q/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201218%2FFYXQRVQFXBAPFLM7FWFS75ZV3Q%2F&d=PGKZrCzpIeFm7bz4D1EKrZKhd8YmQljH21R%2F5cbT5WU%3D&h=83814ef6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201218%2FFYXQRVQFXBAPFLM7FWFS75ZV3Q%2F&h=f84e137d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201218/FYXQRVQFXBAPFLM7FWFS75ZV3Q/</a>"},{"pid":"c14aba7cd315631bc62d9bf9c6ecac34658badfc","tid":2330853,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T10:33:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1567ffb2ff0478749c1a145159b5b6ab62917c96","tid":2330853,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T10:35:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4338b24188f4fb3ab9d76d676af706227416151a","tid":2330853,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy